snippet.title: One Piece Odyssey - Announcement Trailer
snippet.description:
A storm, a shipwreck, a mysterious island.
Expect the unexpected on your next adventure with the Straw Hats!

ONE PIECE ODYSSEY is coming to PS5 & PS4, Xbox Series X|S and PC in 2022.
